          <div class="shmd-info-grid">
            <div class="shmd-info-item full-width">
              <span class="shmd-label">ลิงก์ปลายทาง</span>
              <a id="shmd-link-val" href="#" target="_blank" class="shmd-link-text">-</a>
            </div>
            <div class="shmd-info-item">
              <span class="shmd-label">จำนวนสั่งซื้อ</span>
              <span id="shmd-qty-val" class="shmd-value-bold">-</span>
            </div>
            <div class="shmd-info-item">
              <span class="shmd-label">จุดเริ่มต้น</span>
